		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />would writing to a name table not currently being rendered cause glitches? or do all writes to vram durring non-vblank time cause errors?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
