	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It doesn't matter <em>which</em> nametable (or pattern table) is being accessed - the fact that one is being accessed at all means you cannot mess with $2006/$2007 during rendering without causing problems.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
